::Mosquitor::

Mosquitor frowns in confusion, looking down at Black Arachnia. "The 
leadership left you in charge?" he asks a bit doubtfully, looking at her. The 
doubt dissapeared as the part about Rampage registered in his slow mind.

"Rampage has taken over agains orders?" Mosquior asks, a trace of anger in 
his voice, "We mush follow the leadership's commands! We have to restore you 
to rule!" Mosquitor pauses, a bit proud of his conclusion. He takes out his 
gun, completely forgetting about Black Arachnia and running off toward the 
bridge.
